.modal.fade(tabindex="-1", role="dialog")
  .modal-dialog
    form.modal-content
      .modal-header
        button(type="button", class="close", data-dismiss="modal") &times;
        h3.modal-title WebRTC Not Supported

      .modal-body
        p
          | The collaboration features uses a new technology called 
          a(href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/WebRTC") WebRTC
          | .

        p Unfortunately, not every browser supports it. For the best support try 
          a(href="https://www.google.com/intl/en/chrome/browser/") Chrome
          |  or
          a(href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/") Firefox
          | . For more information, check out 
          a(href="http://iswebrtcreadyyet.com/") isWebRTCreadyyet.com
          |.

        p
          | If your browser doesn't support WebRTC, you can always go to 
          a(href='/') the home page
          |  and enter your own bracket.

      .modal-footer
        a.btn.btn-primary(href="/") Back to Home Page